{"title":"css文字换行缩进","date":"2019-09-04T08:48:55.000Z","link":"post/css文字换行缩进","tags":["css"],"updated":"2019-09-04T08:55:15.971Z","content":"<h3 id=\"文字自动换行缩进\">文字自动换行缩进<a href=\"post/css文字换行缩进#文字自动换行缩进\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight css\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-tag\">text-indent</span><span class=\"selector-pseudo\">:-3em</span>;<span class=\"comment\">/* 缩进 其实是首行向左移动，造成首首行一下的文字有缩进的效果 */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-tag\">margin-left</span><span class=\"selector-pseudo\">:3em</span>;<span class=\"comment\">/* margin-left:复位 可以不设置 */</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"/post/css文字换行缩进/Snipaste_2019-09-04_16-54-34.png\" alt=\"css文字缩进\" class=\"article-img\"></p>\n","next":{"title":"tips","link":"post/tips"},"plink":"http://yoursite.com/post/css文字换行缩进/"}